Class JWildExpression

  • java.lang.Object
    • jminusminus.JAST
      • jminusminus.JStatement
        • jminusminus.JExpression

  •  class JWildExpression
extends JExpression
    The AST node for a "wild" expression. A wild expression is a placeholder expression, used when there is a syntax error.
